Class Server

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, play.db.Model
@Entity
public class Server
extends play.db.jpa.Model

An instance of a server represents one of the chat servers that the master server will utilize to spawn new chat rooms, and also will be used to assign heart beat servers to.
